Add Additional Repositories: Add repositories for additional software like Packman for multimedia codecs.


sudo zypper ar -cfp 90 http://packman.inode.at/suse/openSUSE_Tumbleweed/ packman
sudo zypper dup --from packman


Install Multimedia Codecs

sudo zypper install --from packman gstreamer-plugins-bad gstreamer-plugins-ugly
sudo zypper install --from packman ffmpeg

